text: Kuzebekovo () is a rural locality (a village) in Novochebenkinsky Selsoviet, Zianchurinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 157 as of 2010. There are 6 streets. == Geography == It is located 20 km from Isyangulovo, 12 km from Ishemgul. == References == Category:Rural localities in Zianchurinsky District
title: Kuzebekovo
